(6, 5, 'John', 'John34e@gmail.com', '', '197.231.221.211', '2015-03-22 06:44:39', '2015-03-22 06:44:39', 'The decision by the Staten Island grand jury not to indict Officer Daniel Pantaleone heightened tensions that have simmered in the city since the July 17 death of Eric Garner. In the neighborhood where Garner died, people reacted with angry disbelief and chanted, I cant breathe! and Hands up - dont choke', 0, '0', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/35.0.1916.153 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0),
